<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1436,151,213]" pageId="14" pageNumber="465">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,151,177]" pageId="14" pageNumber="465">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was originally recorded from northern 
<collectingCountry box="[934,1029,151,177]" name="Vietnam" pageId="14" pageNumber="465">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
(Tam Dao). 
<bibRefCitation author="Yamaya, S. &amp; Muramoto, R." box="[1183,1436,151,177]" pageId="14" pageNumber="465" pagination="1 - 34" refId="ref17677" refString="Yamaya, S. &amp; Muramoto, R. (2008) On the genus Eophileurus Arrow, 1908 (Scarabaeidae, Dynastinae), with descriptions of five new species. Kogane, Supplement 2, 1 - 34." type="journal article" year="2008">Yamaya &amp; Muramoto</bibRefCitation>
(2008) firstly reported this species from 
<collectingCountry box="[604,674,187,213]" name="China" pageId="14" pageNumber="465">China</collectingCountry>
, which is confirmed here with additional records.
</paragraph>
